(13, '32', 'Resep Minuman Kekinian', 'resep-minuman-kekinian', 'Kelas Online Membuat Ratusan Menu Kekinian', '<h4>Resep apa saja yang akan kamu dapatkan?<br>Â </h4><ul><li><p><strong>Iced Latte (Tanpa Kopi)</strong></p><p>Palm Sugar Cheese<br>Ice Milk Chocolate<br>Es Kopi Susu Gula Aren Mimu - Mimu<br>Iced Blend Milky Regal<br>Frappe Sweet Potato<br>Choco Apple Iced Latte<br>Choco Almond Iced Latte<br>Sweet Black Garlic Latte<br>Fresh Strawberry Ice Latte Cassava<br>Avocado Iced Latte<br>Japanesse Iced Latte<br>Ice Palm Cappuccino<br>Royal Choco Iced Latte<br>Romantic Menu \"Sweet Talk\"<br>Red Vevlet Iced Latte<br>Choco Banana Iced Latte / Piscok Iced Latte<br>Mocca Rumme Iced Latte<br>Choco Butter Scotch Iced Latte<br>Black Velvet Iced Latte<br>Choco Caramel Iced Latte<br>Black Forest Iced Latte</p></li><li><p><strong>Mocktail (Tanpa Alkohol)</strong></p><p>Mocktail MboWis<br>Heavy Bold Tiramisu<br>Grapefuit Pressolve Fruitoccino<br>Orange Mocktail<br>Dragon Coco Pea<br>Halloween Mocktail<br>Berry Mint Lime Mocktail<br>Apple Espresso Martini Mocktail<br>Santa\'s Backyard Mocktail<br>Cucumber Rose</p></li><li><p><strong>Signature</strong></p><p>Boba Choco dengan Almond Milk<br>Klepon Dragon Ice Blend<br>Watermelon Hydro</p></li><li><p><strong>Garnish</strong></p><p>Coral Tuile<br>Garnish Jeruk Nipis<br>Fresh Garnish<br>Tuile Charcoal<br>Garnish dari Sisa Kulit Jeruk<br>Coconut Latte Art<br>Apple Garnish<br>Egg Foam</p></li><li><p><strong>Ice with Coffee</strong></p><p>Affogato<br>Ice Palm Cappuccino<br>Mocca Frutta Strawberry Latte<br>Long Hydro<br>Banana Ice Latte<br>Watermelon Coffee Fizz<br>Salted Caramel Banana Bitter<br>Creamy Spicedchai Coffee Fizz<br>Butter Scotch Banana Bitter<br>Signature Banana Bitter<br>Cheese Cream Ice Latte</p></li><li><p><strong>Tea</strong></p><p>Caramel Iced Tea<br>Japanesse Matcha Iced Latte</p></li><li><p><strong>Latte Art</strong></p><p>Pouring Latte Art 1<br>Norit Charcoal Latte Art<br>Latte Art Hack 1<br>Latte Art Hack 2<br>Pou